RISKS AND MITIGATIONS

Risk: Key talent departure during transition
Mitigation: Retention conversations, clear career paths, possible retention bonuses

Risk: Productivity dip during transition
Mitigation: Protect Prism launch timeline, defer non-critical work

Risk: Premature information leak
Mitigation: Limited distribution, confidentiality reminders, quick timeline

Risk: Team morale impact
Mitigation: Transparent communication, "no layoffs" commitment, team building

